        { "tests/test_stress_job_concurrency", "job queue stress", "Verify concurrent producers and close-versus-submit races drain every accepted job exactly once and release all parked workers.", "Run this under TSAN first; inspect queue admission, publish-before-post ordering, and close wake permits if a count drifts or a producer stalls." },
